trans-unit.source: Represents the name of a queue associated with an event on a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowInstance"></xref>.
This class cannot be inherited.
This class can be associated with a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.WorkflowQueue> or any other queues used by the Workflow Foundation (WF).
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.EventQueueName"></xref> class by using the specified <xref href="System.Type"></xref> and operation name.
The <xref href="System.Type"></xref> of the interface to associate with the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.EventQueueName"></xref>.
A string that contains the name of the operation to associate with the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.EventQueueName"></xref>.
